comments: Rivers (DEN) is moving alongside DeRozan's (CHI) path and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Caruso (CHI) firms up in his screening position in Rivers' (DEN) path and absorbs the contact.
Rivers (DEN) steps forward into LaVine's (CHI) path and initiates body and head contact with LaVine on the perimeter.
LaVine (CHI) brings his off-arm toward Rivers' (DEN) front and marginal contact occurs as LaVine releases away from the contact.
DeRozan (CHI) avoids making contact with Barton (DEN) as he contests the driving shot attempt.
Dozier (DEN) moves laterally with his arm extended forward and initiates contact with DeRozan's (CHI) side and arm as he attempts to cut back toward the basket after his gather.
Gordon (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Ball's (CHI) path and absorbs the contact. Gordon and Ball then engage and disengage with one another as the pick expires.
Green (CHI) turns slightly toward Campazzo (DEN) and marginal body contact occurs as Campazzo dribbles toward the sideline.
Ball (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position as Gordon (DEN) backs him down in the post and Ball then legally contests Gordon's jump shot attempt.
LaVine (CHI) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Rivers (DEN) extends his hands forward and initiates contact with DeRozan's (CHI) side and back during the drive.
Green (CHI) brings his hands toward Gordon's (DEN) hip and back and quickly releases as Gordon turns to roll toward the lane.
Dozier (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Ball's (CHI) path and absorbs the contact.

Gordon (DEN) and Green (CHI) engage and disengage with one another following the release of the shot attempt and they each make clean contact with the ball as simultaneous incidental contact occurs during rebounding.
Green (CHI) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Denver.
Caruso (CHI) contests Barton's (DEN) jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Barton's right forearm after the release.
Dozier (DEN) moves laterally into DeRozan's (CHI) body and delivers contact as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Caruso (CHI) and Gordon (DEN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Green (CHI) and Barton (DEN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Green (CHI) legally contests Barton's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Campazzo (DEN) brings his arm down and marginal contact occurs with DeRozan's (CHI) right arm as he secures the rebound.
Dozier (DEN) brings his hand up and makes contact with DeRozan's (CHI) arm prior to making any contact with the ball.
Caruso (CHI) moves alongside Barton's (DEN) path and marginal body contact occurs as Barton dribbles along the sideline.
